            <section class="my-8 py-2">
                <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="Fallback with Initials" class="scroll-mt-20">
                    Fallback with Initials
                </RzHeading>
                <RzParagraph TextColor="SemanticColor.Foreground">
                    If <code class="font-semibold">AvatarImage</code> has no source or fails to load, <code class="font-semibold">AvatarFallback</code> renders its child content (e.g., initials).
                </RzParagraph>

                <RzBrowser class="my-4">
